'''孕酮受体'''（{{lang-en|progesterone receptor}}，缩写'''PR'''，也被称为'''NR3C3''' ，nuclear receptor subfamily 3, group C, member 3，即[[核受体|核受体]]第三亚族C组成员3）是一种细胞内蛋白质，由[[甾体激素|甾体激素]][[孕酮|孕酮]]激活。

在人体中，孕酮受体由[[基因|基因]]''PGR'' 编码，位于11号染色体长臂22区<ref name="pmid3551956">{{cite journal | author = Misrahi M, Atger M, d'Auriol L, Loosfelt H, Meriel C, Fridlansky F, Guiochon-Mantel A, Galibert F, Milgrom E | title = Complete amino acid sequence of the human progesterone receptor deduced from cloned cDNA | journal = Biochem. Biophys. Res. Commun. | volume = 143 | issue = 2 | pages = 740–8 |date=March 1987 | pmid = 3551956 | doi = 10.1016/0006-291X(87)91416-1 | url = | issn = }}</ref><ref name="pmid3472240">{{cite journal | author = Law ML, Kao FT, Wei Q, Hartz JA, Greene GL, Zarucki-Schulz T, Conneely OM, Jones C, Puck TT, O'Malley BW | title = The progesterone receptor gene maps to human chromosome band 11q13, the site of the mammary oncogene int-2 | journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. | volume = 84 | issue = 9 | pages = 2877–81 |date=May 1987 | pmid = 3472240 | pmc = 304763 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.84.9.2877| url = | issn = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://may2009.archive.ensembl.org/Homo_sapiens/Gene/Summary?g=ENSG00000082175 |title=ensembl.org, Gene: ESR1 (ENSG00000091831) |access-date=2014-06-28 |archive-date=2022-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105075227/http://may2009.archive.ensembl.org/Homo_sapiens/Gene/Summary?g=ENSG00000082175 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，能通过选择性剪接形成两种蛋白异形体A和B，有着各自不同的分子量<ref name="pmid15970482">{{cite journal | author = Gadkar-Sable S, Shah C, Rosario G, Sachdeva G, Puri C | title = Progesterone receptors: various forms and functions in reproductive tissues | journal = Front. Biosci. | volume = 10 | issue = | pages = 2118–30 | year = 2005 | pmid = 15970482 | doi = 10.2741/1685 }}</ref><ref name="isbn0-683-30379-1">{{cite book | author = Kase, Nathan G.; Speroff, Leon; Glass, Robert L. | title = Clinical gynecologic endocrinology and infertility | url = https://archive.org/details/clinicalgynecolo0000sper | publisher = Lippincott Williams & Wilkins | location = Hagerstown, MD | year = 1999 | pages = | isbn = 0-683-30379-1 | oclc